    %p This searches catalog records for archival collections in six repositories:
    %ul
      %li=link_to "Avery Library, Department of Drawing & Archives", "http://archivesportal.cul.columbia.edu/repository.php?r=nnc-a"
      %li=link_to "Burke Library Archives at Union Theological Seminary", "http://archivesportal.cul.columbia.edu/repository.php?r=nnc-ut"
      %li=link_to "Columbia University Archives", "http://archivesportal.cul.columbia.edu/repository.php?r=nnc-ua"
      %li=link_to "Health Sciences Library Archives & Special Collections", "http://archivesportal.cul.columbia.edu/repository.php?r=nnc-m"
      %li=link_to "Rare Book & Manuscript Library", "http://archivesportal.cul.columbia.edu/repository.php?r=nnc-rb"
      %li=link_to "Starr East Asian Library Rare Books & Special Collections", "http://archivesportal.cul.columbia.edu/repository.php?r=nnc-ea"

    %p Archival collections include personal papers, institutional records, corporate archives, architectural drawings, printed ephemera, realia, and many other types of content.

    %p This source searches:
    %ul
      %li finding aids
      %li collection descriptions
      %li available digital content, such as online exhibits and images



